<h3 id="org3873d67">Permanent Notes</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org3873d67">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Each card has a single unit of knowledge</li>
<li>Use your own words !</li>
<li>Brief and concise</li>
<li>Practice writing well</li>
</ul>

<p>
Should capture all thought provoking idea from all sources.
